Generate a MASVS Assessment Report
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand the OWASP Mobile Application Security Verification Standard (MASVS) framework
Conduct static security analysis on Android APK files
Develop Python scripts to automate security assessments
Generate professional security assessment reports in Markdown format
Document security findings using structured templates
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of Android application structure
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic security assessment concepts
Knowledge of Markdown formatting
Lab Environment
Al Nafi provides ready-to-use Linux-based cloud machines for this lab. Click Start Lab to access your pre-configured environment with all necessary tools installed.

Task 1: Set Up MASVS Assessment Environment
Step 1.1: Install Required Tools
# Update system and install dependencies
